<div ana="#b3" corresp="#beth0124.translation" subtype="transcription" type="edition" xml:id="beth0124.transcription">
<p>Ἰάδις εὔμυρος,<lb/>
<unclear>Σ</unclear>α<unclear>μ</unclear>ουήλου υἱὼς<lb/> Ἰωσῆ, Σαμουῆλος
						διδάσ<supplied reason="lost">καλος</supplied>
</p>
</div>
<div ana="#b3" corresp="#beth0124.transcription" type="translation" xml:id="beth0124.translation">
<p>
<persName ref="persons.xml#beth0124p01" xml:lang="hbo ">Iadis</persName>, <rs ana="interpretations.xml#lot" type="formula">good lot</rs>. <name type="patr">Of <persName ref="persons.xml#beth0124p02" xml:lang="hbo ">Samuel</persName>, (his) <rs ana="interpretations.xml#son" type="family">son </rs>
<persName ref="persons.xml#beth0124p03" type="patr" xml:lang="hbo ">Yose </persName>
</name>. (This is the grave) of Samuel, the <rs ana="interpretations.xml#teacher" type="religTitle">teacher</rs>. </p>
</div>
</body>
<back>
<div type="commentary">
<p>Catacomb 8, Hall A, room VII, above arcosolium 2.  There were multiple additions to this inscription.</p>
</div>
